OL,4,CCovid: Restaurants get creative in bid
OL,5,Cto plug staff shortage
OL,6, Restaurant group Hawksmoor is offering
OL,7, bonuses of up to #2,000 to workers who
OL,8, recommend friends for jobs in a bid to
OL,9, fill staffing shortages.
OL,11,FAnother chain has emailed customers
OL,12,Fwith a promise of gift vouchers if they
OL,13,Fintroduce candidates who go on to be
OL,14,Fhired by the firm.
OL,16,FIt comes as the hospitality sector
OL,17,Ffaces a jobs crisis that threatens to
OL,18,Fhold back its recovery.
OL,20,FHawksmoor co-founder Will Beckett told
OL,21,Fthe BBC there "aren't enough people".
